title: Bug 21187[Working Sets] WorkingSetManager sending bogus property change event
description: Bug 21187[Working Sets] WorkingSetManager sending bogus property change event Add back when this bug isfixed.
OB: build R2.0The WorkingSetManager.removeWorkingSet sends a CHANGEWORKINGSETREMOVE eventeven if a removed working set does not exist in the list of working sets.WorkingSetManager.removeWorkingSet should ignore the remove request when theworking set does not exist.Commented out failing test case inIWorkingSetManagerTest.testAddPropertyChangeListener.
